story:
Find all high school students who speak English and have passed all their subjects, 
but are currently marked as inactive in the system.
Identify inactive high school students proficient in English who have successfully completed all subjects.
Find high school students who are proficient in English but are currently inactive and have passed all their subjects.
Seek out high school students who are skilled in English, currently not engaged, and have successfully completed all their coursework.
Find proficient high school students in English who are currently inactive and have finished all their coursework.
Identify skilled high school students in English who are not currently engaged and have completed all their assignments.
